{"tid":729080,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［君要臣死］海航57歲創辦人王健意外離世","createTime":"2018-07-04T09:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T09:52:05.000Z","uid":18720,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"916bfe84ee270428c298ff45fa5aba19bc7a79e4","tid":729080,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"海航集團聯合創辦人、董事長王健，在法國公務考察時意外跌落導致重傷，經搶救無效，於當地時間2018年7月3日不幸離世，享年57歲。<br />\n<br />\n據彭博資料，王健早年曾經在內地官方航空部門工作，90年代與其他數名人士創辦海航，於2000年起在海航出任行政總裁一職，後於2013年起任主席，屬於集團中的決策者。<br />\n<br />\n外媒引述公開文件稱王健持有海航15%股份。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180704/58398784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180704%2F58398784&d=DmzLgRHuwX6UFhEYtwJOottKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=3b79627b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180704%2F58398784&h=f43a50a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180704/58398784</a>"},{"pid":"c2e84a419539a34a55577cb7d8cdee9d1196a322","tid":729080,"uid":18720,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/171442_35feefd3fd3edbdbc3ff3d1a6ac96d65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F171442_35feefd3fd3edbdbc3ff3d1a6ac96d65.png&h=6a3c2242&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9826fcc21ec4da8cd2d26041fb1d5a04890fe379","tid":729080,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:15:59.000Z","msg":"咁撚兒戲"},{"pid":"67ecb7456c6022fe1374018a45975c91f9515356","tid":729080,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:16:40.000Z","msg":"意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e5ab5